description:
Check out the new ProArt PX13 from ASUS Here: https://asus.click/px13_drew

In Japan, there is a fish called FUGU that is so poisonous that it kills several people every year. I have been anxious to try it and learn more about the preparation process that goes on behind the scenes, so join me on this crazy adventure to see what we can discover!  Along the way, we take a few pit stops around Japan to try more of the bizarre foods that this country offers - so if you are the type to get squeamish, then consider yourself warned!!

#travel #food #japan
